    <item>
      <title>特朗普在棕榈滩向富有的捐赠者试镜副总统候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/trump-auditions-vp-picks-before-wealthy-donors-in-palm-beach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)借鉴了他主持真人秀节目《学徒》(The Apprentice)的经历，本周末在富有的捐助者面前展示了竞选搭档的最佳竞争者，从而加强了他对可能的竞选搭档的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/trump-auditions-vp-picks-before-wealthy-donors-in-palm-beach</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 17:01:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其确认因加沙战争而停止与以色列的所有贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/turkey-halts-all-trade-with-israel-officials</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名知情官员周四早些时候表示，土耳其确认将停止与以色列的所有贸易，直到以色列允许不间断且充足的人道主义援助流入加沙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/turkey-halts-all-trade-with-israel-officials</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 15:12:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普陪审团听到他在秘密录音带上与科恩讨论付款问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/trump-argues-gag-order-bars-him-from-responding-to-rude-posts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普封口费刑事审判的陪审团听取了一段秘密录音，其中这位前总统在 2016 年大选前几个月与当时的律师迈克尔·科恩讨论了一笔付款问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/trump-argues-gag-order-bars-him-from-responding-to-rude-posts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 15:09:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
